OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FA woman with a disability, from
OL,7,FKendal, says she feels "targeted" and
OL,8,Fhas "concerns over what the future may
OL,9,Flook like" following the UK
OL,10,FGovernment's plan to slash disability
OL,11,Fbenefits by #5bn.
OL,13,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,14,FKendall outlined major changes to the
OL,15,Fbenefits system on 18 March 2025 -
OL,16,Fwith the aim to get more people
OL,17,Fworking and save #5bn by 2030.
