OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FThe amount of people claiming sickness
OL,7,For disability benefit has risen from
OL,8,F2.8m to 4m across England and Wales
OL,9,Fsince 2019.
OL,11,FThe proposals include tightening the
OL,12,Fcriteria for disability benefits,
OL,13,Fscrapping a work capability
OL,14,Fassessment, raising the basic rate of
OL,15,Funiversal credit and also cutting the
OL,16,Fhighest rate for those too ill to work.
