OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FCaroline Howsley, Chief Executive of
OL,7,Fthe Cumbria Deaf Association, has
OL,8,Fnumerous long-term conditions which
OL,9,Finclude rheumatoid arthritis,
OL,10,Fosteoarthritis and fibromyalgia.
OL,12,FShe said: "None of these things are
OL,13,Fgoing to get better. So to know that
OL,14,Fmy support network, which is the
OL,15,Fpayment, may be taken away, it does
OL,16,Fconcern me because I wonder what it
OL,17,Flooks like for the future.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
