OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,F"I was told ten years ago I'd be in a
OL,7,Fwheelchair by now and I made a
OL,8,Fdetermined effort to make sure that
OL,9,Fwas not going to be my future.
OL,11,F"In five to ten years from now I
OL,12,Fprobably will be at some point, but
OL,13,Fsometimes I'll be using a walking
OL,14,Fstick, other days will be crutches-
OL,15,F disability varies day to day."
