OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FDuring Prime Minister's Questions
OL,7,F(PMQs) today (19 March 2025), Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer said he
OL,9,Funderstands the impact of disability
OL,10,Fthrough his mother and brother. He
OL,11,Fadded: "But the current system is
OL,12,Fmorally and economically indefensible.
OL,13,FWe are right to reform it and nobody
OL,14,Fshould be defending the broken status
OL,15,Fquo.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
