OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,F"We are proceeding on three
OL,7,Fprinciples: if you can work, you
OL,8,Fshould work; if you need help into
OL,9,Fwork, the state should help you, not
OL,10,Fhinder you; and if you can never work,
OL,11,Fyou must be supported and protected.
OL,13,F"They are the right principles, and we
OL,14,Fcannot leave the current system as it
OL,15,Fis."
OL,17,FMs Howsley says Personal Independent
OL,18,FPayments (PIP) have helped pay for
OL,19,Fmobility aids and adaptations in her
OL,20,Fhome.
