OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FShe said: " It's paid for disabled
OL,7,Fpersons Railcard; it's paid for me to
OL,8,Fbuy Blue Badge and parking tests. It's
OL,9,Famazing how quickly all these things
OL,10,Fadd up.
OL,12,F"Every time you have to go to hospital
OL,13,Fto be treated - I go to Preston
OL,14,Fregularly. So from Kendal down
OL,15,FPreston, it's about #60 every visit.
OL,16,FAnd that's a lot of money that's
OL,17,Fcoming out of your wages every month.
OL,18,FI'm not saying PIP is an addition to
OL,19,Fmy wage, it's there as a necessity to
OL,20,Fhelp me stay well so I can continue in
OL,21,Fwork."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
