OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of Cumbria Deaf
OL,7,FAssociation says the recent debate
OL,8,Fsurrounding disability is "beginning
OL,9,Fto affect me and other service users".
OL,11,FShe added: "People are judging us
OL,12,Fwithout even understanding what the
OL,13,Fdisability that we have is or how it
OL,14,Faffects us, what it costs to be
OL,15,Fdisabled.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
