OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,F"The changes make me feel unsettled
OL,7,Fand unnerved, and it does make me feel
OL,8,Flike I'm being targeted. I work full
OL,9,Ftime. I've always worked full time and
OL,10,FI've been contributing through
OL,11,Fvoluntary work for many, many years.
OL,12,FSo I feel like I'm adding to society.
OL,14,F"PIP enables me to go to work. It
OL,15,Fkeeps me fit and well, but with the
OL,16,Fthings that enable me to keep moving
OL,17,Fas well as I can.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
