OL,3,CWoman speaks out on Government plans
OL,4,Cto slash disability benefits
OL,6,F"If PIP's taken away from me, then I
OL,7,Fwill get to the point where I might
OL,8,Fnot be able to work full time. I might
OL,9,Fhave to go part time, and then the
OL,10,FGovernment will have to start paying
OL,11,Fme to top up my wages, which doesn't
OL,12,Fmake any sense.
OL,14,F"They ought to be putting across a
OL,15,Fmore positive message that we're not
OL,16,Ftrying to stop people scrounging.
OL,17,FWe're trying to enable an enhanced
OL,18,Flife for those that really need it.
OL,19,FThat should be the message.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
